===''Naruto True Stories'' series===

{{nihongo|'''''Naruto True Stories'''''|NARUTO -ナルト- 真伝|Naruto Shinden}} is a [[light novel]] trilogy illustrated by [[Masashi Kishimoto]], which explores [[Itachi Uchiha]]'s past and [[Sasuke Uchiha]]'s future. The ''Naruto True Story'' novels were announced in June 2015, with a publication date in Fall 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://j-books.shueisha.co.jp/pickup/naruto_shinden/|title=NARUTO -ナルト- 真伝｜JUMP j BOOKS|publisher=[[Shueisha]]|accessdate=March 2, 2017}}</ref> [[Viz Media]] began publishing English translations of the novels in November 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-04-14/viz-media-licenses-naruto-itachi-story-tokyo-ghoul-novels-gangsta-cursed-manga/.101057|title=Viz Media Licenses Naruto: Itachi's Story, Tokyo Ghoul Novels, Gangsta.: Cursed Manga|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|accessdate=March 2, 2017}}</ref>
